enhanced_by.reason: Initialization of fields in OpenApiDiff is necessary to ensure all dependencies are properly set up before performing the diff.
Pre-processing the OpenAPI specifications can help in normalizing the data before the diff operation, ensuring more accurate comparisons.
The method getResponseDiff().diff() performs a similar comparison operation on individual ApiResponse objects, which can inform the assertions for the diff method.
The method getExtensionsDiff().diff() handles the comparison of extensions, which is a part of the diff method's responsibility, and can inform the assertions for the diff method.
